transformations

Class Transform_Identity

  • java.lang.Object
    • transformations.Transform_Identity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITransform

    public class Transform_Identity
extends Object
implements ITransform
    Transform that simply turns a state into an array of numbers and back. No state reduction occurs. This is primarily useful as a placeholder or a testing tool. Note that the x component of the body is subtracted out in transform.
    Author:
    Matt
